\f1\b0\fs42 \cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}6 tablespoons unsalted butter\
{\listtext	\'95	}1 cup honey\
{\listtext	\'95	}2 tablespoons distilled white {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/vinegar/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 vinegar}}\
{\listtext	\'95	}2 tablespoons Worcestershire sauce\
{\listtext	\'95	}1/2 cup chopped pecans\
{\listtext	\'95	}2 tablespoons ground {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/ancho-chile/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 ancho chile}}* (or chipotle powder)\
{\listtext	\'95	}2 teaspoons garlic powder\
{\listtext	\'95	}Salt and freshly ground black pepper\
   \'95	2 pounds {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/chicken/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 chicken}} drumettes\
